    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">OnlyFans: The Market Leader</h2>
      
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Strengths:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>✅ <strong>Largest user base:</strong> 3M+ creators, 200M+ users</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Brand recognition:</strong> Most mainstream awareness</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Simple interface:</strong> Easy for new users</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Established payment processing:</strong> Reliable payouts</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Weaknesses:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>❌ <strong>20% creator fee:</strong> Higher than some alternatives</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>Limited tier options:</strong> Single subscription price only</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>No public discovery:</strong> Creators must self-promote</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>Banking restrictions:</strong> Some content types flagged</li>
      </ul>

