        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Creators set one subscription price ($5-$50/mo typical). Subscribers pay that monthly fee + optional PPV content. OnlyFans takes 20% of all earnings.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Fansly: The Feature-Rich Alternative</h2>
      
