      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Strengths:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>✅ <strong>Lower fees:</strong> 5% (Lite) to 12% (Pro) vs. OnlyFans 20%</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Built-in discovery:</strong> Explore page, search, categories</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Community features:</strong> Polls, comments, Discord integration</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Mainstream appeal:</strong> No NSFW stigma for creators</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Weaknesses:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>❌ <strong>No NSFW allowed:</strong> Strict content policy (nudity banned)</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>Creator-focused UX:</strong> Subscribers find it less intuitive</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>Payment processing fees:</strong> Additional 2.9% + $0.30 per transaction</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        <strong>Target audience:</strong> Artists, podcasters, YouTubers, educators—anyone creating non-adult content who wants a lower platform fee and better discovery.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
