        <li><strong>Best for:</strong> Creators who prefer selling content à la carte vs. subscriptions</li>
        <li><strong>Subscriber benefit:</strong> Buy specific clips without monthly commitment</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">LoyalFans</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Focus: Live streaming + subscriptions. Better live interaction tools than OnlyFans.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Best for:</strong> Creators who do frequent live shows (cam-style content)</li>
        <li><strong>Fee:</strong> 20% (same as OnlyFans)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">JustForFans</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Focus: LGBTQ+ creators and content. Smaller, more niche community.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li><strong>Best for:</strong> Gay/queer creators and fans seeking targeted community</li>
        <li><strong>Fee:</strong> 25% (higher than OnlyFans)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
