        <li>You want access to the largest creator pool</li>
        <li>You follow creators who only use OnlyFans</li>
        <li>You prefer simple, familiar interface</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Choose Fansly if:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>You want more flexible tier options (Basic/Premium/VIP)</li>
        <li>Your favorite creators use both (try Fansly for better features)</li>
        <li>You like follow-for-free models (lower commitment)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Choose Patreon if:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>You support non-adult creators (artists, podcasters)</li>
        <li>You want community features (polls, comments, Discord)</li>
        <li>You prefer built-in discovery (easier to find new creators)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6">Choose ManyVids if:</h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>You prefer buying individual clips vs. monthly subscriptions</li>
        <li>You want à la carte purchasing (no recurring billing)</li>
        <li>You're interested in cam shows + live interaction</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Multi-Platform Strategies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Many creators use multiple platforms simultaneously. As a subscriber, this means:
      </p>
      
