      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        For most adult content subscribers, <strong>OnlyFans remains the best overall choice</strong> due to its massive creator pool and simple UX. However:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Try <strong>Fansly</strong> if your favorite creators offer multi-tier pricing there</li>
        <li>Use <strong>Patreon</strong> for non-adult creators (artists, educators, podcasters)</li>
        <li>Check <strong>ManyVids</strong> if you prefer buying clips vs. subscriptions</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-gray-700">
        The best strategy: Use OnlyFans as your primary platform, but don't hesitate to explore alternatives when specific creators offer better value elsewhere.
